---

## Classification Color Codes

| Classification | Background Color | Border Style |
|----------------|-----------------|--------------|
| Confidential | #4A4A4A | Thin gray |
| Secret | #8B0000 | Double red |
| Top Secret | #FFD700 | Embossed gold |
| Cosmic Secret | #9400D3 | Animated purple glow |

## Rarity Visual Indicators

| Rarity | Effect |
|--------|--------|
| Common | None |
| Uncommon | Subtle paper texture |
| Rare | Faint watermark visible |
| Epic | Occasional glitch effect |
| Legendary | Pulsing aura, particle effects |

## Redaction Visual Representation

Redaction is represented visually by:
- Black bars over text in the image
- Percentage displayed as "█" blocks (e.g., 70% = ███████░)
- Animated scanlines suggesting censorship
- Occasional frame where redaction flickers, revealing glimpses

## Heinousness Visual Representation

- Score 1-3: Clean document, white background
- Score 4-6: Slight yellowing, coffee stains
- Score 7-8: Blood spatter texture, burn marks
- Score 9: Darkened edges, ominous shadow overlay
- Score 10: Constant subtle static, occasional scream audio on interaction

## Interactive Elements

### On Hover:
- Redaction bars shift slightly (tease reveal)
- Classification stamp rotates 3D
- Skill icon pulses

### On Click:
- Full-screen document view
- "Attempt Decryption" minigame option
- "Equip" button (if owned)
- "Trade" button linking to marketplace

### On Long Press:
- Reveal hidden metadata (if high enough player level)
- Show connected document web
- Display conspiracy theory connections

